| **Link**    | **Method** | **Input**                                                                   | **Output**                                                                                      | **Working**                                                                                   |
| ----------- | ---------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `/register` | POST       | `ProfileDTO` (JSON)<br>→ `fullName`, `email`, `password`, `profileImageUrl` | `ProfileDTO` (JSON)<br>→ `id`, `fullName`, `email`, `profileImageUrl`, `createdAt`, `updatedAt` | Registers a new user. Password is hashed. Account is marked active. Activation email is sent. |
| `/login`    | POST       | `AuthDTO` (JSON)<br>→ `email`, `password`                                   | JSON containing:<br>`token` (JWT),<br>`user` (ProfileDTO without password)                      | Authenticates user. Verifies credentials. Generates JWT token. Sends back user details.       |
| `/health`   | GET        | *None*                                                                      | `"OK"` or some basic server status message                                                      | Simple health check endpoint for testing if the server is up.                                 |
